---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Vechornytsi handles the information you share when you book, shop, or join a waitlist.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 md:pt-24 pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-[52rem]">
      <span class="kicker">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05] mt-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="container-reading flex flex-col gap-5 text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <p>We keep only what we need to seat you, ship your order, or text you when a seat opens. Your email and phone number are used to reply to inquiries, confirm bookings, and — if you opt in — send drop alerts and waitlist notifications.</p>
      <p>Payments are handled by Wix's secure hosted checkout; we never see or store your card details. Waitlist and inquiry details are stored with Wix and are not sold or shared.</p>
      <p>Ask us to see, correct, or delete your information any time at <a href="mailto:tanyazavodenko188@gmail.com" class="text-accent">tanyazavodenko188@gmail.com</a>. Reply STOP to any text to stop SMS.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
